---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<section class="intro">
  <p class="intro-eyebrow">Data &middot; Software &middot; Math</p>
  <h1>Shane<br><em>Ausmus.</em></h1>
  <p>
    Data strategy and GTM engineer at Verkada. Former McKinsey analyst.
    Vanderbilt economics &amp; CS. I write about software, math, and whatever
    else I'm working through.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <p class="label">Recent Posts</p>
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | head(5) %}
    <li class="post-row">
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <div class="post-row-right">
        {% if post.data.category %}<span class="tag">{{ post.data.category }}</span>{% endif %}
        <span class="date">{{ post.date | shortDate }}</span>
      </div>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
